ZH: 昨天发生了一场严重的火灾。
EN: A serious fire broke out yesterday.

ZH: 消防队员正在全力扑灭火灾。
EN: Firefighters are working hard to extinguish the fire.

ZH: 这场火灾造成了巨大的财产损失。
EN: The fire caused huge financial losses.

ZH: 家里的电线老化引发了火灾。
EN: The aging electrical wires in the house caused the fire.

ZH: 火灾威胁到了附近的居民。
EN: The fire threatened nearby residents.

ZH: 不要用明火附近，以免引发火灾。
EN: Do not use open flames nearby to prevent fires.

ZH: 这座建筑因为火灾变成了废墟。
EN: The building turned into ruins due to the fire.

ZH: 消防队在火灾中表现英勇。
EN: The fire brigade showed great courage in the fire.

ZH: 着火了，立刻报警！不要让火灾蔓延。
EN: Call the police immediately when a fire occurs! Do not allow the fire to spread.

ZH: 在野外露营时，要注意火灾预防。
EN: When camping in the wilderness, be sure to prevent wildfires.

ZH: 火灾发生时，要保持镇静，不要慌乱。
EN: Stay calm and do not panic when a fire breaks out.

ZH: 学校定期组织防火演习，提高师生的应急反应能力。
EN: Schools regularly conduct fire drills to improve staff and students' emergency response capabilities.

ZH: 火灾烧毁了许多文物，是不可挽回的损失。
EN: The fire destroyed many cultural relics, which is irreparable loss.

ZH: 居民向政府呼吁加强火灾预防意识。
EN: Residents call on the government to strengthen awareness of fire prevention.

ZH: 火灾警报发出后，大家应该迅速撤离危险区域。
EN: After the fire alarm sounds, everyone should evacuate the dangerous area quickly.

ZH: 火灾的起因可能是短路或人为纵火。
EN: The cause of the fire may be short circuit or arson.

ZH: 消防队员冒着生命危险救援火灾现场。
EN: Firefighters risk their lives to rescue the scene of the fire.

ZH: 火灾发生时，家庭成员应该一起协作，保障安全。
EN: When a fire occurs, family members should cooperate together to ensure safety.

ZH: 这次火灾是由于燃气泄漏引起的。
EN: This fire was caused by a gas leak.

ZH: 政府在火灾后提供了灾后重建援助。
EN: The government provided post-disaster reconstruction assistance after the fire.
